    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3">Business Structure Options</h3>

    <div class="space-y-4 mb-6">
      <div class="border-l-4 border-blue-500 pl-4">
        <h4 class="font-semibold text-neutral-900">Einzelunternehmen (Sole Proprietorship)</h4>
