        <p class="text-red-700 font-medium">Application rejected. IHK found no clear economic benefit—business plan too vague, no demonstrated expertise, no evidence of market demand. Reapplied 6 months later with specific niche, professional certifications, and letters of intent from potential clients. Second application approved. Lesson: German authorities want concrete plans, not general ideas.</p>
